# EXE packaging — Local build & Cloud CI

## Trigger gate

Active only if any of these exists at repo root: `scripts/watch-build-release.ps1`, `scripts/build-release.ps1`, `scripts/build_exe.ps1`, `scripts/pack-ready.ps1`, `scripts/ci_and_build.ps1`, or a `.csproj`/`.sln` whose docs state a shipped desktop `.exe`. Otherwise write `EXE packaging: N/A (no build script, no shipped .exe)` in the Done check and skip.

## Local mode — MUST

When `MODE: Local` and this task touched `src/`, `ui/`, `wwwroot/`, or any packaging script (and the user did not say "docs only / no build"):

1. Run one release build: `.\scripts\watch-build-release.ps1 -Once`. Fallback order if primary is absent: `.\scripts\build-release.ps1 -Mode self-contained` → `.\scripts\build_exe.ps1` → `.\scripts\ci_and_build.ps1`.
2. If `dist/` is locked, stop the running app and retry.
3. Report `.exe` full path and LastWriteTime in your final message.

## Cloud mode — MUST

You cannot run a Windows desktop `.exe` here.

1. Confirm `.github/workflows/` has a workflow that builds the release `.exe` on `windows-latest` (e.g. `build-release-exe.yml` calling `scripts/build-release.ps1`).
2. Missing in an EXE repo → add a minimal Windows workflow in this task. Path filters must include `src/`, `ui/`, `scripts/build-release.ps1`, the `.sln`/`.csproj`. Template: `templates/github-workflow-build-release-exe.yml`.
3. After push, verify that workflow triggered and reaches `success` per `post-push-ci-green.mdc`.
4. State in handoff: `Local exe not built here; verified via CI run <id>.`

## You MUST NOT

- Skip the build because "the change was just a merge" if `src/` or `ui/` actually changed.
- Mark cloud work done when only Ubuntu jobs are green and the Windows EXE job is missing or red.
- Change `.exe` output path, WebView2/wwwroot layout, or `models/` paths without updating the project's documentation in the same task.

## This repo (array-mic-refreshment)

**Active** — `scripts/watch-build-release.ps1` and `scripts/build-release.ps1` exist.

| Workflow | File | Purpose |
|----------|------|---------|
| CI | `.github/workflows/ci.yml` | `build-and-test` (Linux) + **`build-windows`** (App.Tests) |
| Release EXE | `.github/workflows/build-release-exe.yml` | `build-release.ps1` on `windows-latest` |

Release build also runs `ui/` → `npm ci && npm run build` before publish. Log: `dist\watch-build.log`. If `dist/` locked, stop `ArrayMicRefreshment` process first.
